{"tid":1558939,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支持止暴制亂 舉報暴力行爲","createTime":"2019-09-10T15:26:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:41:06.000Z","uid":312441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c8f0694d64f07200e890f2718df84cfd760dcae5","tid":1558939,"uid":312441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/70513676_10218116335692324_110231774465884160_o_yUeeA_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F70513676_10218116335692324_110231774465884160_o_yUeeA_1200x0.png&h=9278680c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//警方今日公布，將設立 10 條「反暴力報料熱線」，經 whatsapp 接收涉及「暴力」的匿名報料，包括資料、相片、錄音，提供新渠道「希望市民同警隊一齊止暴制亂」。<br />\n<br />\n警察業務科高級警司陳志勇表示，警方接收市民資訊的方式一直有改變，50 年代推出 999 熱線，之後亦有罪案郵簡，以至近年電子報案室；由於過去 3 個月社會動蕩不安，明白渴望社會回復平靜的市民，希望有渠道可以向警方提供消息，決定推出「反暴力報料熱線」，將會有 10 個 whatsapp 號碼，接收「止暴制亂訊息」，不需要事先登記，號碼由 5566 9500 開始連續的 10 個號碼。<br />\n<br />\n陳志勇表示，熱線只會接收「反暴力情報」，不會接聽任何來電，亦不會交代任何案件，不適用於一般報案，若有緊急情況或報案，市民應該繼續致電 999 緊急熱線。//<br />\n<br />\n見到以下呢啲鼓吹暴力嘅言論或行爲，我哋一定唔可以姑息養奸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D9ClkFVVAAAGhmf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD9ClkFVVAAAGhmf.jpg&h=67a026c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/462618241197347/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F462618241197347%2F&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4VhCriQ9KcwZROA2Rh0I8Zw%3D&h=8539ce36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/462618241197347/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php49MB3j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php49MB3j.jpg&h=e67a953f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">立即發送「反暴力情報」！全力支持警察工作！齊做良好公民！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">舉報熱線：</span><br />\n5566 9500<br />\n5566 9501<br />\n5566 9502<br />\n5566 9503<br />\n5566 9504<br />\n5566 9505<br />\n5566 9506<br />\n5566 9507<br />\n5566 9508<br />\n5566 9509<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不妨forward晒去呢10條熱線，確保警方一定睇到！</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只接Whatsapp! 唔聼電話!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"32a682bb915fd6d8de9ebcbb69e390995041b7d7","tid":1558939,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:41:06.000Z","msg":"[超合作運動] 全球齊篤灰 #wtsappforhk #standwithhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拉埋外國勢力齊篤灰順便宣傳警暴</strong></span></span>"}]}